        building UI components intuitive and readable.
      </p>

      <h2>What is JSX?</h2>
      <p>
        JSX looks like HTML, but it is actually JavaScript. When your code
        runs, JSX gets transformed into regular JavaScript function calls
        that create React elements.
      </p>

      <pre><code>{`// This JSX:
<h1>Hello, World!</h1>

